Package: vote
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Real-time voting application
 Vote Coloré is a real-time voting system with WebSocket support.
 It allows trainers to create voting sessions and trainees to vote
 on predefined colors. Features include multiple choice support,
 real-time statistics, and automatic reconnection.
